#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:8
msgid "Finishing the upgrade process from 1.3.13 to 1.6"
msgstr "Fin de la procédure de mise à jour 1.3.13 vers 1.6"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:8
msgid ""
"backup, backing up, restoring, restore, server, WAPT, private key, Code "
"Signing, waptupgrade, documentation"
msgstr ""
"Sauvegarder, Restaurer, serveur, WAPT, clé privée, Code Signing, waptupgrade, "
"documentation"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:16
msgid "Defining a password for the Administrator's private key"
msgstr "Définir un mot de passe sur la clé privée"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:18
msgid ""
"The WAPT console has lost the path to the private key, it is normal because "
"in 1.3 the WAPT console was pointing to the private key. Now in 1.5, the WAPT "
"console points to the certificate associated with the private key."
msgstr ""
"La console a perdu le chemin vers sa clé privée, c'est normal dans la version "
"1.3, la console pointait vers la clé privée. Depuis la version 1.5, la "
"console pointe vers le certificat associé à la clé."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:23
#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:86
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Tools --> Preferences --> Path to personal "
"certificate`, then fill in the path to the new certificate."
msgstr ""
"Rendez-vous donc dans :menuselection:`Outils --> Préférences --> Chemin du "
"certificat personnel` et sélectionner le certificat issue de votre clé privée "
"existante :"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:30
msgid "Select the private key certificate"
msgstr "Sélectionner le certificate de la clé privée"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:32
msgid ""
"WAPT 1.6 requires to protect the private key with a password to sign packages "
"and actions."
msgstr ""
"WAPT 1.6 nécessite un mot de passe sur la clé privée utilisée pour la "
"signature des paquets et des actions."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:35
msgid ""
"In the WAPT console, go to :menuselection:`Tools --> Change the password of "
"the private key`, then select your certificate and enter a password for your "
"private key."
msgstr ""
"Dans la console, aller dans :menuselection:`Outils --> Changer le mot de "
"passe de la clé privée` puis sélectionnez votre certificat et choisissez un "
"mot de passe pour la clé privée."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:40
msgid "Generating a *Code Signing* certificate"
msgstr "Générer un certificat *Code Signing*"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:42
msgid ""
"WAPT 1.6 differentiates **Code Signing** certificates from simple **SSL** "
"certificates."
msgstr ""
"WAPT 1.6 différencie maintenant les certificats **Code Signing** des "
"certificats **SSL** simples."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:45
msgid "It is therefore necessary to regenerate a **Code Signing** certificate."
msgstr "Il faut donc regénérer un nouveau certificat **Code Signing**."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:47
msgid ""
"By default, WAPT 1.6 Community generates self-signed **Code Signing** "
"certificates."
msgstr ""
"Par défaut, WAPT 1.6 Community Edition génère des certificats Code Signing "
"autosignés."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:50
msgid ""
"You must insure that the old certificate in :file:`C:\\private\\mykey.crt` "
"and the key :file:`C:\\private\\mykey.pem` are present in :file:`C:\\private`."
msgstr ""
"Vous devez vous assurer que l'ancien certificat :file:`c:\\\\private\\\\wapt-"
"private.crt` et la clé :file:`c:\\\\private\\\\wapt-private.pem` sont "
"présents dans :file:`c:\\\\private`."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:55
msgid ""
"For packages to be deployed on the :term:`Organization`'s computers, all "
"packages will have to be re-signed with a *Code Signing* certificate."
msgstr ""
"Pour permettre l'installation des paquets sur les ordinateurs de l':term:"
"`Organisation`, il faudra donc resigner tous les paquets en utilisant un "
"certificat *Code Signing*."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:58
msgid ""
"To create the *Code Signing* certificate, in the WAPT console go to :"
"menuselection:`Tools --> Generate a certificate`."
msgstr ""
"Pour créer ce certificat, dans la console WAPT aller dans :menuselection:"
"`Outils -->Générer un Certificat`."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:65
msgid "Code Signing certificate"
msgstr "Certificat Code Signing"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:69
msgid ""
"Normally, you will not have to recreate a new key. Only the certificate will "
"have to be changed. **You must enter the path to your key** (ex: :file:`C:"
"\\private\\mykey.pem`)."
msgstr ""
"Normalement, vous n'avez pas à recréer une nouvelle clé. Seul le certificat "
"sera changé. Dans chemin de la clé, **vous devez indiquer** votre clé :file:"
"`c:\\private\\wapt-private.pem`."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:75
msgid ""
"Do not make changes to the informations on the certificate. If any "
"information is changed, then you will not be able to migrate from 1.3.13 to "
"1.6 using the :program:`waptupgrade` procedure."
msgstr ""
"Ne modifiez pas les informations du certificat. Si cette information est "
"modifée, la mise à jour 1.3.13 vers 1.6 ne pourra pas être faite avec WAPT et "
"le paquet :program:`waptupgrade` ne fonctionnera pas !"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:79
msgid ""
"The WAPT console now asks you whether the new certificate should be added to "
"the :file:`ssl` folder of the local WAPT agent, you can accept."
msgstr ""
"La console vous demande maintenant si ce nouveau certificat doit être ajouté "
"dans le dossier :file:`ssl` de l'agent WAPT, vous pouvez accepter."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:82
msgid ""
"Now that you have generated your new key you must now change the path to your "
"personal certificate. The WAPT console must now point to this new certificate."
msgstr ""
"Maintenant que vous avez généré votre nouvelle clé, vous devez à nouveau "
"modifier le chemin vers le certificat personnel. La console doit maintenant "
"pointer vers ce nouveau certificat."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:93
msgid "New Code Signing certificate"
msgstr "Nouveau certificat Code Signing"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:95
msgid "You may now delete the old certificate."
msgstr "Vous pouvez maintenant supprimer l'ancien certificat."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:98
msgid "Re-signing the packages on your WAPT repositories"
msgstr "Re-signer les paquets du dépôt"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:100
msgid ""
"**All WAPT 1.3.13 must be re-signed** because WAPT 1.6 packages must be "
"signed with a *Code Signing* certificate and hashed with sha256."
msgstr ""
"**Les paquets 1.3.13 doivent être re-signés** avec la nouvelle procédure 1.6 "
"qui intègre le certificat *Code-Signing* dans le paquet et utilise "
"l'algorithme de hachage sha256."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:104
#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:229
msgid "Linux"
msgstr "Linux"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:106
msgid ""
"You must temporarily copy your private key (:file:`.pem`) and the *Code "
"Signing* certificate (:file:`.crt`) on your Linux based WAPT Server using :"
"program:`WinSCP` or an equivalent tool."
msgstr ""
"Transférer temporairement votre clé privée (:file:`.pem`) et le certificat "
"**Code-Signing** (:file:`.crt`) sur le serveur WAPT en utilisant :program:"
"`WinSCP` ou un utilitaire équivalent."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:114
msgid "Temporarily upload your Code Signing certificate on the WAPT server"
msgstr ""
"Téléchargez temporairement votre certificat Code Signing sur le serveur WAPT"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:116
msgid ""
"Then, connect with SSH to the Linux WAPT Server and re-sign all WAPT *base* "
"packages with the new certificate:"
msgstr ""
"Se connecter en SSH sur le serveur, re-signer les paquets *base* en précisant "
"le chemin du certificat :"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:125
msgid ""
"The WAPT Server :term:`SuperAdmin` password is requested to access the "
"database so to do the matching between :term:`FQDN` and their corresponding :"
"term:`UUID` ."
msgstr ""
"Le mot de passe :term:`SuperAdmin` du serveur est demandé pour accéder à la "
"base de données pour établir la correspondance entre les :term:`FQDN` et les :"
"term:`UUID`."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:129
msgid "Rename host packages with the UUID nomenclature:"
msgstr "Renommer les paquets machine au format de nommage UUID :"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:137
#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:167
msgid ""
"The private key now password protected, the password is requested for signing "
"the packages."
msgstr ""
"La clé privée étant désormais protégée par un mot de passe, le mot de passe "
"est demandé pour re-signer les paquets."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:142
#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:172
msgid "**DO NOT FORGET** to delete the private key (.pem) from the WAPT Server!"
msgstr ""
"N'oubliez pas de **SUPPRIMER la clé** (:file:`.pem`) du serveur après avoir "
"re-signé les paquets !"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:145
#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:238
msgid "Windows"
msgstr "Windows"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:147
msgid ""
"Then, open a session on the Windows machine hosting the WAPT Server and re-"
"sign all WAPT base packages with the new certificate:"
msgstr ""
"Se connecter en SSH sur le serveur, re-signer les paquets *base*  en "
"précisant le chemin du certificat :"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:156
msgid ""
"The WAPT Server :term:`SuperAdmin` password is requested to access the "
"database so to do the matching between FQDNs and their corresponding UUIDs."
msgstr ""
"Le mot de passe :term:`SuperAdmin` du serveur est demandé pour accéder à la "
"base de données."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:159
msgid "Rename *host* packages with the UUID nomenclature:"
msgstr "Renommer les paquets *host* au format de nommage UUID :"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:175
msgid "Generating the PostgreSQL database table for the group packages"
msgstr "Générer la table des dépendances groupe"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:177
msgid ""
"In WAPT 1.3, group filtering was done by scanning the :file:`Packages` index "
"file in the :file:`wapt-host` folder of the WAPT Server."
msgstr ""
"Dans la version 1.3 de WAPT, le filtrage par groupe était effectué en "
"parcourant le fichier :file:`Packages` du dossier :file:`wapt-host` du "
"serveur."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:180
msgid ""
"For performance reasons, the filtering is now done by querying a PostgreSQL "
"database table. The table will fill in automatically as WAPT agents register "
"with the WAPT Server 1.6."
msgstr ""
"Pour des raisons de performance, ce filtrage est maintenant géré en "
"parcourant une table PostgreSQL. Cette table sera alimentée au fur et à "
"mesure en version WAPT 1.6."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:184
msgid ""
"To quickly regenerate the database table, the trick is to create a temporary "
"group *mig-temp*."
msgstr ""
"Pour regénérer rapidement cette table, l'astuce consiste a créer un groupe "
"*mig-temp* dans WAPT."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:187
msgid ""
"You may then apply the *mig-temp* package to all WAPT clients from the WAPT "
"console (:kbd:`CTRL+A` in the inventory, then :menuselection:`Right-click --> "
"Add dependencies` and select the package *mig-temp*)."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez ensuite appliquer le paquet *mig-temp* à tous les clients WAPT "
"depuis la console WAPT (:kbd:`CTRL+A` dans l'inventaire, puis :menuselection:"
"`Clic droit --> Ajouter en dépendance` et sélectionnez le paquet *mig-temp*)."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:192
msgid ""
"You may now revert the operation (:kbd:`CTRL+A` in the inventory, then :"
"menuselection:`Right-click --> Remove dependencies` and select the package "
"*mig-temp*)."
msgstr ""
"Faire l'opération inverse. (:kbd:`CTRL+A` dans l'inventaire, puis :"
"menuselection:`Clic-droit --> Supprimer des dépendances` et sélectionner *mig-"
"tempo*)."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:196
msgid "The filtering of groups should be operational again."
msgstr "Le filtrage groupe devrait à nouveau fonctionner."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:199
msgid "Ugrading WAPT agents"
msgstr "Mettre à jour les clients WAPT"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:201
msgid ""
"You may now follow the procedure to :ref:`create the new WAPT agent "
"<create_WAPT_agent>`."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez maintenant suivre la :ref:`procédure pour créer l'agent WAPT "
"<create_WAPT_agent>` !!"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:206
msgid "The version update implies a change in the way packages are signed."
msgstr "Le changement de branche modifie le mode de signature."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:208
msgid ""
"If you update from 1.3.13, the WAPT package :program:`waptupgrade` should "
"install correctly if you check the box :guilabel:`sign waptupgrade with "
"sha256 AND sha1` while generating the WAPT agent."
msgstr ""
"Si vous mettez à jour depuis la version 1.3.13, le paquet :program:"
"`waptupgrade` devrait s'installer correctement si vous cochez la case :"
"guilabel:`signer waptupgrade en sha256 ET sha1` lors de la génération de "
"l'agent wapt."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:212
msgid ""
"If your WAPT agents are in a version that is less than 1.3.13, the package :"
"program:`waptupgrade` **will not work**."
msgstr ""
"Si vos agents sont dans une version inférieure à 1.3.13, le paquet :program:"
"`waptupgrade` **ne fonctionnera pas**."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:215
msgid ""
"You may choose instead to use a :command:`waptdeploy` GPO to :ref:`deploy the "
"new WAPT agent on your installed base of PCs <install_waptagent>`."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez mettre en place une GPO :command:`waptdeploy` pour :ref:`déployer "
"le nouvel agent WAPT sur votre parc <install_waptagent>`."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:220
msgid "Installing waptupgrade on the computers"
msgstr "Lancer l'installation de waptupgrade sur les clients"

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:222
msgid ""
"With version 1.6, it is no longer possible to directly contact WAPT agents in "
"an inferior version from the WAPT console."
msgstr ""
"Dans la version 1.6 il n'est plus possible de contacter les clients < 1.6 "
"depuis la console WAPT."

#: ../../source/waptserver_update/migration13-16/suite-upgrade.rst:225
msgid ""
"To allow you to install the *waptupgrade* package on 1.3.13 computers, we "
"have designed a small script."
msgstr ""
"Pour vous permettre de lancer l'installation du paquet *waptupgrade* sur les "
"1.3 nous avons prévu un petit script."

